node.text:
We’re celebrating #WhiskeyWednesday the Proper way with
this glazed salmon recipe from @getprimefish 

4 tbsp Proper No. Twelve Irish Whiskey
1 tsp ginger, minced
1 tsp garlic, minced
2 tbsp apple cider vinegar
2 tbsp soy sauce
¼ cup brown sugar
2 tbsp honey

In small saucepan over medium heat combine all ingredients. Whisk mixture
until combined and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to a simmer and stir
constantly until the mixture thickens and reduce by half, 3-5 minutes.

Introducing the Proper Watermelon Cooler 🍉🥃 Mix up the recipe below to celebrate #WhiskeyWednesday and enjoy by the pool like @thenotoriousmma 

1 part Proper No. Twelve Irish Whiskey
3 parts watermelon juice
.5 part lime juice
Sprig of mint
Slice of fresh watermelon

Combine Proper No. Twelve, watermelon juice and lime juice in a shaker and strain into a tall glass with ice. Garnish with mint and watermelon slice. 
*Proper Tip: blend this up with ice for a frozen version
